<p>Hi {{merchantName}},</p>
<p>Your fiat settlement of <strong>{{settlementAmount}} {{settlementCurrency}}</strong> has been sent to your bank account.</p>
<div class="detail-box">
  <table>
    <tr><td>Reference</td><td>{{reference}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Crypto Received</td><td>{{amount}} {{currency}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Settlement Amount</td><td>{{settlementAmount}} {{settlementCurrency}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Bank Account</td><td>{{bankAccount}}</td></tr>
    <tr><td>Settled At</td><td>{{settledAt}}</td></tr>
  </table>
</div>
<p>Funds typically arrive within 1–2 business days depending on your bank.</p>
